0080|- [HelpText]
0081|*When making Flash demos, activations and mouse clicks can be
0082|*recorded by inserting a line
0084|*act_sounds=SUR_ACT,SUR_ML,SUR_MR
0086|*in the SURVO.APU file. The default WAV files listed above are
0087|*in the directory <Survo>\U\SND.
S   |                  <     >
0088|*After making this modification and restarting Survo, the sounds
0089|*are activated by keystrokes F2 L E and deactivated by F2 L e.
0090|*When the sounds are activated,
0091|*the first sound will heard when a command is activated by ESC or
0092|*a double-click.
0093|*The second sound relates to the mouse click by the leftmost button.
0094|*The third sound relates to the mouse click by the rightmost button.
